egunta.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gracias por su inter\u00e9s y confianza en nuestra instituci\u00f3n.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Atentamente,<\/span><\/p><p><strong>Fiorella Rocha<br \/><em>Admisiones Colegio Gran Breta\u00f1a<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9c22c11 btn-read-more-cgb elementor-tablet-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"9c22c11\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-md\" href=\"\/admissions-step-by-step\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t<svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/1999\/xlink\" id=\"arrow-btn-cgb\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" viewBox=\"0 0 44 16.4\" style=\"enable-background:new 0 0 44 16.4;\" xml:space=\"preserve\"><g id=\"shape\">\t<polygon points=\"44,8.2 35.2,16.4 33.8,14.9 40.5,8.7 0,8.7 0,7.7 40.5,7.7 33.8,1.5 35.2,0  \"><\/polygon><\/g><\/svg>\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">INSTRUCTIONS TO APPLY<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5fc5e43 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"5fc5e43\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-72b6f96 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"72b6f96\" data-element_t